{"id":232859098,"title":"每個人心裡都有一個 Joker 小丑，我們該怎麼辦？《Joker 小丑》解說","content":"Joker 小丑\n每個人心裡都有一個Joker\n底層的人繼續日復日的機械式工作 受盡欺壓\n我們「表層」的Joker就像這張圖 只能壓抑、嘀咕\n但這樣的Joker只會一直折磨自己\n阿瑟要重回正軌，變回「正常」人\n不再受同事欺壓 不再受暴力的束縛\n不再活在母親的陰霾下 不再受所有人的嘲笑\n做到這樣「底層」的小丑可能會很危險\n因為固有的經驗、價值觀會塌陷\n要走出舒適圈 探索未知的世界\n但我們應該要怎樣自處和安身立命呢？\n\n每個人心裡都有一個 Joker 小丑，我們該怎麼辦？《Joker 小丑》解說\nhttps://youtu.be/hiI5a6EzTfA","excerpt":"Joker 小丑，每個人心裡都有一個Joker，底層的人繼續日復日的機械式工作 受盡欺壓，我們「表層」的Joker就像這張圖 只能壓抑、嘀咕，但這樣的Joker只會一直折磨自己，阿瑟要重回正軌，變回「","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"275e0c11-82d0-43df-9606-502f5727716d","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-09T15:04:25.796Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-09T15:05:32.998Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":6,"tags":[],"topics":["小丑","電影","觀後感","影評","Joker"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"電影","forumAlias":"movie","school":"香港教育大學","department":"心理學系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":6}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"de872ce4-b12e-4dba-8baa-f324dedc1586","url":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/hiI5a6EzTfA/hqdefault.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/hiI5a6EzTfA/hqdefault.jpg","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/hiI5a6EzTfA/hqdefault.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-09T15:04:25.796Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-09T15:05:32.998Z"},{"id":"de872ce4-b12e-4dba-8baa-f324dedc1586","url":"https://youtu.be/hiI5a6EzTfA","normalizedUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hiI5a6EzTfA","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/hiI5a6EzTfA/hqdefault.jpg","type":"video/youtube","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-09T15:04:25.796Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-09T15:05:32.998Z"}],"postAvatar":""}